'''Ama Ata Aidoo''', ''née'' '''Christina Ama Aidoo''' (wavutse ku ya 23 Werurwe 1942) ni umwanditsi wo muri [[Gana]], umusizi, umwanditsi w'amakinamico n'umunyeshuri<ref>https://www.britannica.com/biography/Ama-Ata-Aidoo</ref>.  Yari Minisitiri w’uburezi uyobowe na Jerry Rawlings administration <ref>https://literarymama.com/articles/departments/2016/02/a-profile-of-ama-ata-aidoo-draft</ref>. Mu 2000, yashinze Fondasiyo ya Mbaasem yo guteza imbere no gushyigikira umurimo w’abanditsi b’abagore [[Afurika|b’abanyafurika.]]<ref>https://newafricanmagazine.com/3015/</ref>  

== Ubuzima bwo hambere ==
Aidoo yavutse ku ya 23 Werurwe 1942 i Saltpond mu mu gace ko hagati muri [[Gana]], Amakuru amwe arimo Megan Behrent, kaminuza ya Brown, na [[Afurika]] Ninde wavuze ko yavutse ku ya 31 Werurwe 1940<ref>https://www.thriftbooks.com/a/ama-ata-aidoo/210811/</ref>. Yakuriye mu rugo rw'umwami wa Fante, umukobwa wa Nana Yaw Fama, umutware wa Abeadzi Kyiakor, na Maame Abasema. <ref>https://www.researchgate.net/publication/39435002_An_interview_with_Ama_Ata_Aidoo_'I_learnt_my_first_feminist_lessons_in_Africa'</ref> Yakuze mugihe cy' [[ubwongereza]] bushya bwa neocolonialism bwaberaga mu gihugu cye<ref>https://www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/arts/features/womenwriters/aidoo_life.shtml</ref>. Sekuru yiciwe na neocolonialiste, ibyo bikaba byaratumye se yibanda ku kamaro ko kwigisha abana n'imiryango yo mu mudugudu n'amateka yabayeho<ref>https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/abs/10.1080/03064229008534948</ref>. Ibi byatumye afungura ishuri rya mbere mu mudugudu wabo maze bituma Aidoo yiga mu ishuri ryisumbuye rya Wesley Girls aho yahisemo bwa mbere ko ashaka kuba umwanditsi<ref>https://www.bookishsanta.com/blogs/booklings-world/books-ama-ata-aidoo</ref>.  

== Uburezi ==
Aidoo yize amashuri yisumbuye ya Wesley Girls i Cape Coast,  kuva 1961 kugeza 1964<ref>https://digitalcommons.unl.edu/unpresssamples/375/</ref>. Amashuri yisumbuye, yiyandikishije muri kaminuza ya Gana, muri Legon aho yakuye impamyabumenyi ya Bachelor of Arts mu Cyongereza ndetse yandika n'ikinamico ye ya mbere yise ''“Dilemma of Ghost”'', mu 1964. <ref>[http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/10410/Ama-Ata-Aidoo "Ama Ata Aidoo"], ''Encyclopædia Britannica''.</ref> Ikinamico yasohowe na Longman umwaka wakurikiyeho, bituma Aidoo aba umukinnyi wa mbere  w’amakinamico wo muri [[Afurika]]. <ref>https://www.degruyter.com/document/doi/10.18574/9781479822607-004/html</ref>

== Filime ==
Niwe filime ya documentaire ya 2014, ''Ubuhanzi bwa Ama Ata Aidoo'', yakozwe na Yaba Badoe . <ref>https://www.ghanaweb.com/person/Ama-Atta-Aidoo-127</ref> <ref>Beti Ellerson, [http://africanwomenincinema.blogspot.co.uk/2013/12/yaba-badoe-talks-about-documentary-film.html "Yaba Badoe talks about the documentary film project 'The Art of Ama Ata Aidoo'"], African Women in Cinema, December 2013.</ref> <ref>Shakira Chambas and Sionne Neely, [http://www.awdf.org/the-art-of-ama-ata-aidoo-documentary-film-launch/ "The Art of AMA ATA AIDOO: Documentary Film Launch"], African Women’s Development Fund, 26 September 2014.</ref>

== Inyandiko ==
Ikinamico ya Aidoo irimo ''The Dilemma of Ghost'', yakorewe i Legon mu 1964 (yatangajwe bwa mbere 1965) na Pittsburgh mu 1988, na ''Anowa'', yasohowe mu 1971 ikorerwa i Londres mu 1991<ref>https://www.kweli.tv/programs/the-art-of-ama-ata-aidoo?locale=en#:~:text=The%20Art%20of%20Ama%20Ata%20Aidoo%20explores%20the%20artistic%20contribution,fascinating%20insight%20into%20her%20life.</ref>. 

